[0m[48;2;40;67;43m[39m+    461[0m:[39m[48;2;24;38;30m [38;2;191;97;106m-[38;2;191;97;106m The split between deterministic fast paths (alias match, NPI lookup, name-shaped) and the LLM slow path in [38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;163;190;140mparse_query[38;2;163;190;140m`[38;2;191;97;106m keeps the median Bedrock cost low without sacrificing the LLM's strength on ambiguous free-text. A reader following the pattern will not accidentally build a "every search calls the LLM" architecture.[K
